The paper deals with entity resolution, which is a common problem in databases and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.DB (Databases) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely categories. The paper also proposes advanced methods that use machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with large datasets and efficient algorithms, which are topics covered in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing, which is a topic covered in cs.CL (Computation and Language).
